divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my back yard and observed a large blaok object comming towards my home from the west heading on an eastward course. As the object come closer it appeared bigger and changed shapes. I had an unobstucted view as the object appeared in a direct path over my home, I watched it until it went out of sight heading over Lake Ray Hubbard towards Rockwall. The sun was going down and as I tried to see where it went, it was no longer sight and could not locate it again.
Summary: Black with no lights or sound, tear drop shape then to a saucer shape
